    "title": "Conditional (continued): Urgency and Attempts",
    "explanation": "Au secours ! — a cry for help. Avril essaye trois fois. — she tries three times. Ça va très mal. — it's going very badly.\n\nNotice très (very) — it intensifies. Très mal = very badly. Très bien = very well.\n\nRe-read and find très. What does it intensify each time? Then find every essayer — what is being attempted?"
